| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0839 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5af7af3d-362b-5ce9-8f80-9176cd30e4ca"
